import { Routes, Route, useHistory } from "react-router-dom";

import HomePage from "./pages/HomePage.js"
import BookDetail from "./pages/BookDetail"
import BookList from "./pages/BookList"
import Cart from "./pages/Cart"
import Complain from "./pages/Complain"
import ComplainAdmin from "./pages/ComplainAdmin"
import Profile from "./pages/Profile"
import Transaction from "./pages/Transaction"

function App() {

  return (
  <Routes>
    <Route path="/" exact element={HomePage} />
    <Route path="/book-detail/:id" exact element={BookDetail} />
    <Route path="/complain" exact element={Complain} />
    <Route path="/profile" exact element={Profile} />
    <Route path="/complain-admin" exact element={ComplainAdmin} />
    <Route path="/book-list" exact element={BookList} />
    <Route path="/transaction" exact element={Transaction} />
    <Route path="/cart" element={Cart} />
  </Routes>
  );
}

export default App;
